<text><body>
<lb n="0774b20" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0774b21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0774b22" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 507</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0774b23" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><note n="0774012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0774012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0774012"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0774013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未生冤＝未生怨【三】下同【宮】</note><note n="0774013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未生冤＝未生怨【宋】下同【元】下同【明】下同【宮】</note><app n="0774013"><lem wit="【大】">未生冤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">未生怨</rdg></app>經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0774b24" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0774b25" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">吳<note n="0774014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔月支國居士〕－【宋】【元】，〔國〕－【宮】</note><app n="0774014"><lem wit="【大】">月支國<note n="0774015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">居士＝優婆塞【明】【宮】</note><app n="0774015"><lem wit="【大】">居士</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【宮】">優婆塞</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">月支居士</rdg></app>支謙譯</byline>
<lb n="0774b26" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0774b2601">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT14p0774b2604" rend="inline">一時，佛在王舍國雞山中。諸天、龍、鬼
<lb n="0774b27" ed="T"/>神、帝王、臣民，皆詣佛所，稽首、承風、供養之
<lb n="0774b28" ed="T"/>儀靡不盡禮。調達覩之，其嫉無量，還告太
<lb n="0774b29" ed="T"/>子未生冤曰：「汝父輦國眾寶以貢佛、諸沙門，
<pb n="0774c" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0507.0774c"/>
<lb n="0774c01" ed="T"/>國藏空竭。可早圖之，即位為王。吾當興師
<lb n="0774c02" ed="T"/>往征佛也。子可為王，吾當為佛。兩得其所，
<lb n="0774c03" ed="T"/>不亦善乎！子必成之。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0774c0309" rend="inline">未生冤與調達結斯
<lb n="0774c04" ed="T"/>陰謀已，則勅秉勢臣令勒兵：「王還，奪其<note n="0774016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝即【明】</note><app n="0774016"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">即</rdg></app>
<lb n="0774c05" ed="T"/>綬以付獄。」王還，臣即如命，以王付獄。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0774c0515" rend="inline">王意
<lb n="0774c06" ed="T"/>恬然，照之宿殃，心無恐懼，重信佛言。王曰：
<lb n="0774c07" ed="T"/>「吾有何過而罪我乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0774c0709" rend="inline">皇后貴人、率土巨細
<lb n="0774c08" ed="T"/>莫不哀慟。王顧謂哭者曰：「佛說天地、日月、須
<lb n="0774c09" ed="T"/>彌山海有成必敗。盛者即衰，合會有離，生
<lb n="0774c10" ed="T"/>者必死。由之憂悲輪轉無際，以致重苦。尋
<lb n="0774c11" ed="T"/>其<note n="0774017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">原＝源【三】【宮】</note><note n="0774017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">原＝源【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0774017"><lem wit="【大】">原</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">源</rdg></app>，察其始，因緣合會即有，謂之生；因緣
<lb n="0774c12" ed="T"/>離散即滅，謂之空。<note n="0774018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夫＝天【宮】</note><app n="0774018"><lem wit="【大】">夫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">天</rdg></app>身者四大耳，眾生魂
<lb n="0774c13" ed="T"/>靈寄處其中。死還其本，魂靈空去，謂之非
<lb n="0774c14" ed="T"/>身。身尚<note n="0774019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（可）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0774019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＋（可）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0774019"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">不可</rdg></app>保，何國之常守乎！佛初入國，吾
<lb n="0774c15" ed="T"/>未有子也。問吾：『寧知當來王不乎？』吾對曰：『不
<lb n="0774c16" ed="T"/>知。』世尊重曰：『一切無常。汝諦思之。』佛之誡
<lb n="0774c17" ed="T"/>我，正為今也。各努力建志，懷存佛誡矣。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0774c1716" rend="inline">王
<lb n="0774c18" ed="T"/>謂太子曰：「汝每有疾，吾為燋心，欲以身命
<lb n="0774c19" ed="T"/><note n="0774020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">救＝受【三】【宮】</note><note n="0774020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">救＝受【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0774020"><lem wit="【大】">救</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">受</rdg></app>危代汝。親之仁恩，<note n="0774021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0774021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0774021"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>天為上。汝懷何
<lb n="0774c20" ed="T"/>心，忍為<note n="0774022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">逆惡＝惡逆【三】</note><note n="0774022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">逆惡＝惡逆【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0774022"><lem wit="【大】">逆惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惡逆</rdg></app>乎？夫殺親者，死入太山，不中
<lb n="0774c21" ed="T"/>止息，汝將當之也。吾是汝尊，重親尊孝尚
<lb n="0774c22" ed="T"/>恐名不稱，豈況殺父乎！以國惠汝，吾欲至佛
<lb n="0774c23" ed="T"/>所作沙門。吾觀婬<note n="0774023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妷＝泆【三】</note><note n="0774023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妷＝泆【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0774023"><lem wit="【大】">妷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">泆</rdg></app>，猶火燒身。女類之好
<lb n="0774c24" ed="T"/>以為虛空，無目之徒靡不惑焉！唯覩佛經，照
<lb n="0774c25" ed="T"/>女偽之尤惡，知榮利之害身。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0774c2512" rend="inline">太子曰：「汝莫
<lb n="0774c26" ed="T"/>多云。吾獲宿願，豈有赦哉！」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0774c2611" rend="inline">勅獄吏曰：「絕其
<lb n="0774c27" ed="T"/>餉食，以餓殺之。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0774c2707" rend="inline">有司將入獄，<note n="0774024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汫＝缾【三】，萍【宮】</note><note n="0774024" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><choice cb:resp="CBETA.maha"><corr>洴</corr><sic>汫</sic></choice>＝缾【宋】【元】【明】，＝萍【宮】</note><app n="0774024"><lem wit="【大】">洴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">缾</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">萍</rdg></app>沙王向佛
<lb n="0774c28" ed="T"/>所在，稽首重拜曰：「子有天地之惡，吾無絲
<lb n="0774c29" ed="T"/>髮之忿心矣。<app type="star" corresp="#0774021"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>存佛教：世無常樂，其苦
<pb n="0775a" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0507.0775a"/>
<lb n="0775a01" ed="T"/>有長。」入獄被髮，仰天呼曰：「痛乎！天豈有斯
<lb n="0775a02" ed="T"/>道哉！」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a0203" rend="inline">后妃貴人、舉國巨細靡不哀慟。后謂
<lb n="0775a03" ed="T"/>太子曰：「大王掠桎梏，處牢獄，坐臥須人，其
<lb n="0775a04" ed="T"/>痛難言。自汝生來，大王赤心，懸情于汝，食
<lb n="0775a05" ed="T"/>息不忘，四大盈<note n="0775001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">縮＝宿【宮】</note><app n="0775001"><lem wit="【大】">縮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">宿</rdg></app>，<note n="0775002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枕＝旃【三】【宮】</note><note n="0775002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">枕＝旃【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0775002"><lem wit="【大】">枕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">旃</rdg></app>伏臨汝，涕泗交并，
<lb n="0775a06" ed="T"/>心燋體枯，欲以身命代爾殞矣。當存天人之
<lb n="0775a07" ed="T"/>育，無為逆也。佛說經云：『夫善之極者，莫大
<lb n="0775a08" ed="T"/>於孝；惡之大<note n="0775003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0775003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0775003"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，其<app type="star" corresp="#0774021"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惟</rdg></app>害親乎！』長幼相事，
<lb n="0775a09" ed="T"/>天當祐之，豈況親哉！汝順<note n="0775004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">凶＝兇【三】</note><note n="0775004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">凶＝兇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0775004"><lem wit="【大】">凶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">兇</rdg></app>虐，為斯重惡，
<lb n="0775a10" ed="T"/>必入太山。世間六十億年為太山一日一夕，
<lb n="0775a11" ed="T"/>所更諸毒，每處有年。汝其畢之，不亦難乎！
<lb n="0775a12" ed="T"/>夫快心之士，無不後悔。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a1210" rend="inline">太子曰：「吾少小有
<lb n="0775a13" ed="T"/>志殺父為王。今日獲願，何諫之云乎！」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a1315" rend="inline">后曰：
<lb n="0775a14" ed="T"/>「夫不用諫者，亡國之基矣！吾欲見大王，寧
<lb n="0775a15" ed="T"/>可不乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a1504" rend="inline">太子曰：「可。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a1508" rend="inline">后淨身澡浴，以蜜<g ref="#CB00595"/>塗
<lb n="0775a16" ed="T"/>身，入見大王面顏瘦痟，不識舉哀。聞之者莫
<lb n="0775a17" ed="T"/>不揮淚。后曰：「佛說榮樂無常，罪苦有恒。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a1716" rend="inline">王曰：
<lb n="0775a18" ed="T"/>「獄吏絕餉食，飢渴日久。身八<note n="0775005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">萬＝十【宮】</note><app n="0775005"><lem wit="【大】">萬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">十</rdg></app>戶戶，有數
<lb n="0775a19" ed="T"/>百種蟲，擾吾腹中。血肉消盡，壽命且窮矣！」
<lb n="0775a20" ed="T"/>言之哽咽，息絕復連。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a2009" rend="inline">后曰：「具照斯<note n="0775006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">艱＝難【三】</note><note n="0775006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">艱＝難【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0775006"><lem wit="【大】">艱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">難</rdg></app>。妾以
<lb n="0775a21" ed="T"/><g ref="#CB00595"/>蜜塗身，可就食之。當惟佛誡無忽也。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775a2116" rend="inline">王
<lb n="0775a22" ed="T"/>食畢，向佛所在，哽咽稽首曰：「佛說榮福難保，
<lb n="0775a23" ed="T"/>如幻如夢，誠如尊教。」謂后曰：「吾為王時，國
<lb n="0775a24" ed="T"/>土廣大，衣食從好。而今處獄，當就餓死。子所
<lb n="0775a25" ed="T"/>從得桀逆之師，違佛仁教。吾不懼死，唯恨不
<lb n="0775a26" ed="T"/>面稟佛清化，與<note n="0775007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鶖鷺＝秋露【宮】</note><app n="0775007"><lem wit="【大】">鶖鷺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">秋露</rdg></app>子、目連、大迦葉講尊
<lb n="0775a27" ed="T"/>道奧耳。」王重謂后曰：「佛說恩愛猶若眾鳥會
<lb n="0775a28" ed="T"/>栖于樹，晨各離散，隨其殃福。目連眾垢已
<lb n="0775a29" ed="T"/>除，諸惡已滅，得<note n="0775008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">于＝大【宮】</note><app n="0775008"><lem wit="【大】">于</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">大</rdg></app>六通、四達，尚為貪嫉梵
<pb n="0775b" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0507.0775b"/>
<lb n="0775b01" ed="T"/>志所捶，豈況吾哉！為殃惡追人，猶影尋身，
<lb n="0775b02" ed="T"/>響之應聲。佛時難遇，<note n="0775009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神化＝佛法【明】</note><app n="0775009"><lem wit="【大】">神化</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛法</rdg></app>難聞，賢眾行高，
<lb n="0775b03" ed="T"/><note n="0775010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">儀式＝儀誡【宮】</note><app n="0775010"><lem wit="【大】">儀式</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">儀誡</rdg></app>無量，非世<note n="0775011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">濡＝俗【明】，儒【宮】</note><note n="0775011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">濡＝俗【明】，＝儒【宮】【麗-CB】【CB】</note><app n="0775011"><lem wit="【CBETA】【麗】" resp="CBETA.maha">儒<note type="cf1">K20n0821_p1134a10</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">濡</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">俗</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">儒</rdg></app>所能履行。懷佛經典，以
<lb n="0775b04" ed="T"/>仁化民；獲供養之福，稟其清化，誠亦難值
<lb n="0775b05" ed="T"/>哉！吾今死矣！遷神遠逝。夫欲建志，莫尚佛
<lb n="0775b06" ed="T"/>教也。汝慎守之，防來禍矣！」后聞王誡，重又
<lb n="0775b07" ed="T"/>哀慟。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775b0703" rend="inline">太子詰獄吏曰：「絕王食有日，不死何
<lb n="0775b08" ed="T"/>為？」對曰：「皇后入獄，有<g ref="#CB00595"/>蜜之貢，以延王命。」太
<lb n="0775b09" ed="T"/>子曰：「自今莫令后見王。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775b0910" rend="inline">王飢，勢起向佛所在
<lb n="0775b10" ed="T"/>稽首，即為不飢，夜時為明。太子聞之，令塞
<lb n="0775b11" ed="T"/>窓牖，削其足底，無令得起而覩佛明。有司
<lb n="0775b12" ed="T"/>即削足底。其痛無量，念佛不忘。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775b1213" rend="inline">佛遙為說經
<lb n="0775b13" ed="T"/>曰：「夫善惡行，殃福歸身，可不慎矣！」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775b1314" rend="inline">瓶沙王
<lb n="0775b14" ed="T"/>對曰：「若當<note n="0775012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">支＝肢【元】【明】</note><app n="0775012"><lem wit="【大】">支</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">肢</rdg></app>解寸斬於體，終不念惡。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775b1415" rend="inline">世尊
<lb n="0775b15" ed="T"/>重曰：「吾今為如來、無所著、正真道、最正覺、道
<lb n="0775b16" ed="T"/>法御、天人師，三千大千日月天神、鬼龍靡不
<lb n="0775b17" ed="T"/>稽首。宿之餘殃，于今不釋，豈況凡庶！」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0775b1715" rend="inline"><note n="0775013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝三【宮】</note><app n="0775013"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">三</rdg></app>受
<lb n="0775b18" ed="T"/>天中天恩，具照宿殃，不敢慍望，不懼<note n="0775014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝太【三】【宮】</note><note n="0775014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大＝太【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0775014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">太</rdg></app>山
<lb n="0775b19" ed="T"/>燒煮之罪，中心在佛及諸弟子，坐臥敢<note n="0775015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忽＝忘【三】【宮】</note><note n="0775015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忽＝忘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0775015"><lem wit="【大】">忽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">忘</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0775b20" ed="T"/>即叉手稽首：「今日命絕，永替神化。」<note n="0775016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喐＝都【宋】【元】，那【明】，噢【宮】</note><note n="0775016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喐＝都【宋】【元】，＝那【明】，＝噢【宮】</note><app n="0775016"><lem wit="【大】">喐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">都</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">那</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">噢</rdg></app>咿哽
<lb n="0775b21" ed="T"/><note n="0775017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咽＝喳【三】【宮】</note><note n="0775017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">咽＝喳【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0775017"><lem wit="【大】">咽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">喳</rdg></app>，斯須息絕。舉國臣民靡不躃踊，呼天奈
<lb n="0775b22" ed="T"/>何。瓶沙王即得道迹，上生天上，三道門塞，
<lb n="0775b23" ed="T"/>諸苦都滅矣！</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0775b24" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0775018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0775018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0775018"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>未生冤<note n="0775019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宋】【元】</note><app n="0775019"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">經一卷</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
